cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper focuses on image captioning, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed architecture is based on a Transformer, which is a type of neural network commonly used in language modeling and falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with multi-modal contexts, which can be related to multimedia (cs.MM).
